data.name: sqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT id, proj_lot_id, pri_id, tax_roll_num, certificate_num, address, assessment, taxes, tax_adj_date, Range, Township, Meridian, Section, Installment1, Installment2, Installment3, Acres FROM PROJ_LOT_TAX_ROLL AS r WHERE (proj_lot_id = @PROJ_LOT_ID) ORDER BY tax_roll_num

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [PROJ_LOT_TAX_ROLL] SET [proj_lot_id] = @proj_lot_id, [pri_id] = @pri_id, [tax_roll_num] = @tax_roll_num, [certificate_num] = @certificate_num, [address] = @address, [assessment] = @assessment, [taxes] = @taxes, [tax_adj_date] = @tax_adj_date, [Range] = @Range, [Township] = @Township, [Meridian] = @Meridian, [Section] = @Section, [Installment1] = @Installment1, [Installment2] = @Installment2, [Installment3] = @Installment3, [Acres] = @Acres WHERE (([id] = @Original_id) AND ([proj_lot_id] = @Original_proj_lot_id) AND ((@IsNull_pri_id = 1 AND [pri_id] IS NULL) OR ([pri_id] = @Original_pri_id)) AND ((@IsNull_tax_roll_num = 1 AND [tax_roll_num] IS NULL) OR ([tax_roll_num] = @Original_tax_roll_num)) AND ((@IsNull_certificate_num = 1 AND [certificate_num] IS NULL) OR ([certificate_num] = @Original_certificate_num)) AND ((@IsNull_address = 1 AND [address] IS NULL) OR ([address] = @Original_address)) AND ((@IsNull_assessment = 1 AND [assessment] IS NULL) OR ([assessment] = @Original_assessment)) AND ((@IsNull_taxes = 1 AND [taxes] IS NULL) OR ([taxes] = @Original_taxes)) AND ((@IsNull_tax_adj_date = 1 AND [tax_adj_date] IS NULL) OR ([tax_adj_date] = @Original_tax_adj_date)) AND ((@IsNull_Range = 1 AND [Range] IS NULL) OR ([Range] = @Original_Range)) AND ((@IsNull_Township = 1 AND [Township] IS NULL) OR ([Township] = @Original_Township)) AND ((@IsNull_Meridian = 1 AND [Meridian] IS NULL) OR ([Meridian] = @Original_Meridian)) AND ((@IsNull_Section = 1 AND [Section] IS NULL) OR ([Section] = @Original_Section)) AND ((@IsNull_Installment1 = 1 AND [Installment1] IS NULL) OR ([Installment1] = @Original_Installment1)) AND ((@IsNull_Installment2 = 1 AND [Installment2] IS NULL) OR ([Installment2] = @Original_Installment2)) AND ((@IsNull_Installment3 = 1 AND [Installment3] IS NULL) OR ([Installment3] = @Original_Installment3)) AND ((@IsNull_Acres = 1 AND [Acres] IS NULL) OR ([Acres] = @Original_Acres))); SELECT id, proj_lot_id, pri_id, tax_roll_num, certificate_num, address, assessment, taxes, tax_adj_date, Range, Township, Meridian, Section, Installment1, Installment2, Installment3, Acres FROM PROJ_LOT_TAX_ROLL AS r WHERE (id = @id) ORDER BY tax_roll_num

data.name: sqlSelectCommand2.CommandText
data.value: SELECT p.proj_lot_id, p.pri_id, p.year, p.assessment, p.taxes, p.tax_adj_date, p.assessment_id, p.assessment_desc, p.comment, p.id, p.tax_roll_num, p.tax_roll_id, a.Code AS assessment_code, p.Paid FROM PROJ_LOT_TAX_HISTORY AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN LD_Assesment AS a ON a.Assesment_ID = p.assessment_id WHERE (p.tax_roll_det_id = @id) ORDER BY p.tax_adj_date DESC, p.id DESC
